            . I am a <rs id="t18300114-235-viclabel1255" type="occupation">shoemaker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-235-victim1584 t18300114-235-viclabel1255"></join>. On the 9th of December. I was at a back room, which I rent at <placeName id="t18300114-235-crimeloc1256">the Crown in Ratcliff-highway</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300114-235-crimeloc1256" type="placeName" value="the Crown in Ratcliff-highway"></interp>
