                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300114-235-off1253 t18300114-235-crimeloc1256"></join>; I was asleep by the fire, and had six shirts in a bundle on the table - I did not see the prisoner at all; he left the door open when he went out.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300114-235-person1588">
